title: Superman 23.2 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.


Superman 23.2

By:     	Antony Bedard, Pascal Alixe, Gene Ha	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Superhero
Publisher:   	DC Comics	
Pub. Date:  	September 11, 2013
Format:         CBZ

Brainiac was the first adversary Superman fought on Earth, but where did he come from? A lineage that spans the universe holds many secrets when we ask, "Who is Brainiac?"
